908
01:22:35,661 --> 01:22:37,704
It looks like something's going on underneath.

909
01:22:38,465 --> 01:22:44,947
Yeah, it's the soil, Councilor, like I said, it's heavily loaded with clay in that area.

910
01:22:45,727 --> 01:22:51,148
And, you know, it's probably one of the worst types of soil you want to deal with.

911
01:22:51,889 --> 01:23:00,051
But, you know, when we come back in in the spring, all right, and we, you know, scarify and do repaving, we'd be eliminating it at that point in time.

912
01:23:00,866 --> 01:23:07,108
Is there any concern, so when you connect that main on Douglas, that's connecting then to?

913
01:23:07,569 --> 01:23:08,649
