937
01:24:53,011 --> 01:25:02,038
What we would do is we would put in the temporary water lines that would go into the homes, the 32 homes in that street.

938
01:25:02,838 --> 01:25:08,003
And then at that point in time, saw, cut, and excavate a trench exposing the existing pipe.

939
01:25:09,864 --> 01:25:13,287
