2369
03:40:51,220 --> 03:41:03,650
I'm living in a house on piles, as you have just seen, and at the moment you can't close the windows in one side of the house because the whole house is being deformed because of the ground that it's standing on.

2370
03:41:03,810 --> 03:41:07,453
It's getting maybe a thicker active layer or getting more water under there.

2371
03:41:09,140 --> 03:41:16,622
From the Norwegian Polar Institute, Christian Ledesen studies the mammals that spend their entire lives in these arctic waters.

2372
03:41:17,182 --> 03:41:24,903
