2373
03:41:25,603 --> 03:41:30,044
And they are what we call ice associated, two different degrees.

2374
03:41:30,804 --> 03:41:33,505
And the one that is most dependent on sea ice is the ring seal.

2375
03:41:34,165 --> 03:41:45,177
And it's the ringed seal, a small seal with a coat of black spots surrounded by grey rings, that's having a particularly tough time coping with the warm waters around Svalbard.

2376
03:41:45,197 --> 03:41:54,426
They have this very special breathing system where they actually pop in a snow cave on top of a breathing hole in the ice.

2377
03:41:55,487 --> 03:42:01,634
And that protects the very small pup from harsh weather conditions to some degree, but also from predation.

2378
03:42:02,094 --> 03:42:10,383
Because it takes a while for a predator, which is normally a polar bear or a fox, to dig through the layer and take the pup so it has a chance to escape.

2379
03:42:10,903 --> 03:42:25,737
What the problem has been here now the last years is that first, especially on the west side of Spitsbergen, the ice forms very late, if at all, and normally it forms too late for snow, enough snow to accumulate, so they can make these layers.

2380
03:42:27,037 --> 03:42:32,678
And then they pup on the open ice, and then almost all pups are killed before they are weaned.

2381
03:42:32,998 --> 03:42:34,458
Even big gulls take them then.

2382
03:42:35,199 --> 03:42:38,519
In principle, we're not having Arctic conditions here anymore.

2383
03:42:38,539 --> 03:42:40,040
You know, they're changing to more Atlantic.

2384
03:42:41,120 --> 03:42:46,301
And we have here on the west coast of Svalbard, we have harbor seals too, not so ice adapted.

2385
03:42:46,841 --> 03:42:52,222
And it seems like they are thriving with this new Atlantic water, and they're expanding their distribution into the fjords here.

2386
03:42:53,973 --> 03:42:57,796
The oceans at both ends of the world are changing fast.

2387
03:42:58,257 --> 03:43:01,580
Some animals may adapt to warmer waters, others won't.

2388
03:43:03,031 --> 03:43:09,815
