2393
03:43:38,988 --> 03:43:41,928
So yeah, it will change the picture a lot.

2394
03:43:42,568 --> 03:43:49,330
And that could have consequences for a place like this because it could be increased in size considerably if you have ships coming in.

2395
03:43:50,831 --> 03:43:52,334
because Svalbard is positioned there.

2396
03:43:52,454 --> 03:43:57,224
They're actually the hub, the main entrance to cross polar routes.

2397
03:43:58,226 --> 03:44:00,230
So yeah, that's going to be quite interesting to watch.

