03:45:12,636 --> 03:45:21,680
Deep water that fills the bottom of Marianas Trench in the Pacific actually begun its journey into the deep at the sea surface around Antarctica.

2409
03:45:22,141 --> 03:45:26,503
In winter in the Antarctic a lot more of the sea freezes around Antarctica.

