03:45:31,465 --> 03:45:34,226
It effectively doubles the size of the Antarctic.

2412
03:45:34,706 --> 03:45:41,128
And as the surface sea freezes to form that sea ice, it leaves behind very cold, very salty water.

2413
03:45:41,588 --> 03:45:46,929
And that very cold, very salty water is heavier than normal sea water, so it sinks.

2414
03:45:47,989 --> 03:45:52,571
And it sinks and it flows out, spills out from the Antarctic into the deep ocean basins.

2415
03:45:52,651 --> 03:45:57,192
